https://korp.csc.fi/download/finnish-tagtools/v1.3/

download it in the directory you want:
$ wget https://korp.csc.fi/download/finnish-tagtools/v1.3/finnish-tagtools-1.3.2.zip

un-compress it:
$ unzip finnish-tagtools-1.3.2.zip

and install it (as it says its Readme), by going into the un-compressed directory and running the command make on its Makefile file. 
This is:

$ cd finnish-tagtools-1.3.2
$ sudo make install
